{"tid":859693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高鐵西九站food court 4中國人用假證見工被捕","createTime":"2018-10-12T17:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T03:55:29.000Z","uid":39464,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4ba932daf5a260d368bbe77958951f8a87a48fd1","tid":859693,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T17:11:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181012/large/1539355686_49ff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181012%2Flarge%2F1539355686_49ff.jpg&h=5ef6c894&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高鐵西九龍站揭發有內地人持虛假身份證見工，4人被捕。警方接獲相關部門人員報案，稱懷疑4名內地人早前在站內的美食廣場，行使虛假身份證明文件申請工作，以及違反逗留條件。<br />\n<br />\n今午3時許，警員接報到場後，經初步調查，3男1女內地人(23至55歲)涉嫌「行使虛假身份證明文件」及「違反逗留條件」被捕，當中50歲及53歲內地男子亦涉嫌「逾期居留」被捕，現正被扣留調查。案件交由油尖警區刑事調查隊第3隊跟進。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181012/58789124\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181012%2F58789124&d=CqIc3p6sjccGyQYz4AQlkWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=5cd5af6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181012%2F58789124&h=a2bf4dc9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20181012/58789124</a>"},{"pid":"f73b6a4a4f833d073588316e68fec756c2b53ce9","tid":859693,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T17:22:18.000Z","msg":"審完直接扔番大陸啦"},{"pid":"810c955b4ee9d4206dac0955e2251640de4f3932","tid":859693,"uid":65984,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"f73b6a4a4f833d073588316e68fec756c2b53ce9","tid":859693,"uid":14918,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T17:22:18.000Z","msg":"審完直接扔番大陸啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-12T17:35:28.000Z","msg":"虛假文件, 直頭要終身不准入境啦"},{"pid":"6d5937ffae9f5354e0f3